      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>HERSCH-Sophie. On June 24, 2000. Beloved wife of the late Nathan. Loving mother of Arthur, Ira, Stanley and mother-in-law of Jane and Sheila. Cherished grandmother to Jeffrey (Ronny), Jennifer (Daniel), Greer, Meredith (Jonathan) and Matthew. Also survived by six great-grandchildren. Services were held on Monday.</p>
